INSERT INTO `books_shops` VALUES (1,'SALE IN ROME','<p><strong>Saldi (sale)</strong> are starting on the first sunday of January in winter and on the first Sunday of July&nbsp;in summer. During the sales you will find discounts of 30% - 50%. It is important that on every article on sale there is indicated the initial price.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Liquidazioni</strong> - total sale that some shops do before closing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vendite Promozionali</strong> - special promotions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sconti</strong> - discounts.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Entrata libera</strong> - come in to have a look.</p>','saldi.jpg'),(2,'OPENING HOURS','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Usually shops are open between 09.00 - 13.00 and 15.30 - 19.30 (in summer 16.00 - 20.00). In the centre of the city some shops are open from 10.30 till 19.30. On Sundays most of the shops are closed (excluding Christmas time). August is holiday time for Italians. Most of the shops are closed for 2 -3 weeks in August. Ferragosto is celebrated on 15 August. Brand boutiques you will find in Spanish steps district - Via Condotti, Via Frattina, Via Borgognola, Via della Croce and other side streets.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Also, in other districts there are shops with good Italian brands - Via del Corso, Via Nazionale, Via Cola di Rienzo. Big Stores are: La Rinascente, Coin, Gallerea Alberto Sordi.</p>','shops_times.jpg'),(3,'CASLET ROMANO OUTLET','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Castel Romano is really the house of shops and boutiques! Here you will find articles of hiest quality from prestigeous designers, with discounts of 30% - 70%. And all this all year round. It is located at 40 minutes drive from Rome. You will be surprized by the goods represented: international brands, sport goods, accessories, leather goods. And all this just in one place! The space is 25000 m2. You will find there: Asics, Bruno Magli, Calvin Klein, Diesel, Levi\'s, Mandarina Duck, La Perla, Pal Zileri, Pinko, Puma, Reebok, Roberto Cavalli, Salvatore Ferragamo, Valentino and many others. There are many bars, restaurants, children play ground and many other conveniences. The parking is for 2000 cars and you will always find your space. Also, there is the shuttle bus that runs from Rome from Piazza Barberini.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Call 3906 3234705 to book the place one day in advance before 16.00. The price is 21 euro up and down. From monday till thursday bus runs twice a day. Departure from Piazza Barberini at 09.15 and 14.15. Departure back from Castel Romano - 13.00 and 18.00. On Saturday and sunday - once a day. From Piazza Barberini - 09.15 and back from the outlet - 13.00.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Also, at any hotel reception you can book your shuttle bus. You can call 39 06 37350810 or 39 3294317686 one day before the trip. Price - 25 euro up and down ticket. Outlet is open from Monday till Thursday from 10.00 till 20.00. From friday till sunday - from 10.00 till 21.00 You can see more details on <a href=\"http://www.mcarthurglen.it\">www.mcarthurglen.it</a></p>','0'),(4,'VALMONTONE OUTLET','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Valmontone outlet is located at 40 kilometres from Rome. This is the city of shops and boutiques, where you will find GF Ferre, Baldinini, Boticelli, Gaudi, Cacharel, Pacherson, Miss Sixty, Rocco Barocco, Fellini, Pierre Cardin. You will find 30% - 70% discount on dresses, leather, children goods, accessories - all at very convenient prices. </p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"center\">Yoy can reach Valmontone by A1 road (Rome -&nbsp;Naples), uscita to Valmontone and then following signes to Outlet Fashion District.</div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><br /></span></p>','0'),(5,'TAX FREE','<p>In any shop you can pay by cash or credit card. IVA (VAT)&nbsp;is at 12% - for dresses and more than 30% for luxury gods. It is very conveniet to shop in the shops where you can see Tax Free sign.</p>\r\n<p>Tourists from non - european countries can return 15% of tax in the airport or in Tax Free centres in the city when exiting from Italy. Tax free is applicable when you buy for not less than 155 euro.</p>','tax_free.jpg');
